  "title": "ISic000547. I.Sicily inscription 000547",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Noah Cashian</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>d(is) m(anibus) <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[A]ur(elio) · Rustico · mil(itavit) <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ann(os) · VIII tr(iere) (centuria) Zeno-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>nis · Mar(cus) · Germanici-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>anus · mil(itavit) · ann(os) · X <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>Valer(ius) · Victorinus <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>her(es) · b(ene) · m(erenti) · f(ecit) </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Noah Cashian</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>DM<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[.]UR·RUSTICO·MIL<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ANN·VIIITR𐆛ZENO<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>NIS·MAR·GERMANICI<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ANUS·MIL·ANN·X<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>VALER·VICTORINUS<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>HER·B·M·F</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of CIL</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8767-3368\">Noah Cashian</a></p>  <p>To the spirits of the Underworld. Valerius Victorinus, the heir, made this for the well-deserving Aurelius Rusticus, who served for eight years in the century aboard the trireme Zenon, (and for) Marcus Germanicianus, who served for ten years.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Gualtherus 1624 27 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 184 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7288</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a></li><li> Manganaro 1988 41 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\">  Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
